com.authzed.api.v1.LookupResourcesRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
LookupResourcesRequestOrBuilder, com.google.protobuf.Message, com.google.protobuf.MessageLite, com.google.protobuf.MessageLiteOrBuilder, com.google.protobuf.MessageOrBuilder, Serializable
public final class LookupResourcesRequest extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessage implements LookupResourcesRequestOrBuilder
 LookupResourcesRequest performs a lookup of all resources of a particular
 kind on which the subject has the specified permission or the relation in
 which the subject exists, streaming back the IDs of those resources.
Protobuf type authzed.api.v1.LookupResourcesRequest
